  "short_description": "A surreal nightmare by green phosphor and text graphics. But the outdated hardware isn't the only thing that's decaying: devoid of any memories, all you know is a toxin is destroying your body little by little - and it's only one of the things out to kill you. Get ready to die like it's 1981.",
