  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268720/extras/ef8e1051dd319d4163505f7f70e6dac3.avif?t=1736970923\" width=616 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268720/extras/0a65e42aed984b38b9a4e0d9c15abd67.avif?t=1736970923\" width=616 height=300 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >C:\\ type descript.txt</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A surreal nightmare where resisting death is as tempting as it is useless, brought to life by the 256 text characters available on the first PCs.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >C:\\ more</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >What can you do when you wake up in a strange place with your memories wiped out and your hours numbered?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And when you realize this place is a lethal environment, with an impossible geometry created by the processing power of a first-generation PC, which gets even weirder when the floppy drives begin to fail?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >What about those people that seem amused by the fact you're dying by the minute?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And what's with that creature with a taste for human flesh?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Does any of this make any sense? Does that even matter when your time is running out?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Authentic phosphor green gets mixed with not-quite-authentic blood red for results never dreamed of by the monitors of 1981;</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Several ways to make your life even shorter if you're not careful, including electrocution, beheading, getting crushed between walls or eaten by a shark or a gruesome smiling monster;</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268720/extras/830b94e3a8d838de862f41ecf8cdbb6e.poster.avif?t=1736970923\" width=616 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268720/extras/830b94e3a8d838de862f41ecf8cdbb6e.webm?t=1736970923\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268720/extras/830b94e3a8d838de862f41ecf8cdbb6e.mp4?t=1736970923\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268720/extras/ef8e1051dd319d4163505f7f70e6dac3.avif?t=1736970923\" width=616 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268720/extras/0a65e42aed984b38b9a4e0d9c15abd67.avif?t=1736970923\" width=616 height=300 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >C:\\ type descript.txt</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A surreal nightmare where resisting death is as tempting as it is useless, brought to life by the 256 text characters available on the first PCs.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >C:\\ more</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >What can you do when you wake up in a strange place with your memories wiped out and your hours numbered?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And when you realize this place is a lethal environment, with an impossible geometry created by the processing power of a first-generation PC, which gets even weirder when the floppy drives begin to fail?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >What about those people that seem amused by the fact you're dying by the minute?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And what's with that creature with a taste for human flesh?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Does any of this make any sense? Does that even matter when your time is running out?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Authentic phosphor green gets mixed with not-quite-authentic blood red for results never dreamed of by the monitors of 1981;</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Several ways to make your life even shorter if you're not careful, including electrocution, beheading, getting crushed between walls or eaten by a shark or a gruesome smiling monster;</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268720/extras/830b94e3a8d838de862f41ecf8cdbb6e.poster.avif?t=1736970923\" width=616 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268720/extras/830b94e3a8d838de862f41ecf8cdbb6e.webm?t=1736970923\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268720/extras/830b94e3a8d838de862f41ecf8cdbb6e.mp4?t=1736970923\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
